{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"字串運算子","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Expressions_and_Operators_eb65eb8f4e6b3c16f08b95149183cfb8","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<h4 id=\"字串運算子\" name=\"字串運算子\">字串運算子</h4>\n<p>除了比較運算子可以用於字串值以外，連結運算子 (+) 把兩個字串值串連在一起，返回另一個以兩個運算元字串連結的字串。例如，<code>\"my \" + \"string\"</code> 返回<code> \"my string\"</code> 字串。</p>\n<p>代入運算子 += 的簡記法也可用於連結字串。例如，如果變數 <code>mystring</code> 內有 \"alpha\" 值，<code>mystring += \"bet\"</code> 表達式的求值為“alphabet”，並把這個值代入到 <code>mystring</code>。</p>\n<p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/運算子/邏輯運算子\">« 前頁</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/運算子/特殊運算子\">次頁  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"除了比較運算子可以用於字串值以外，連結運算子 (+) 把兩個字串值串連在一起，返回另一個以兩個運算元字串連結的字串。例如，\"my \" + \"string\" 返回 \"my string\" 字串。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"locale":"en-US","title":"Expressions and operators","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/expressions_and_operators_eb65eb8f4e6b3c16f08b95149183cfb8","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/expressions_and_operators_eb65eb8f4e6b3c16f08b95149183cfb8/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide","title":"陣列的運用"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Expressions_and_Operators_eb65eb8f4e6b3c16f08b95149183cfb8","title":"字串運算子"}],"pageTitle":"字串運算子 | MDN","noIndexing":true}}